{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_09",
  "title": "星見編2章35話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ならいっそ――自分自身がその人になっちゃえば\nいいって思いますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why don’t you just pretend you’re her?\nI think that would work for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.889385002851486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 5.793650913238525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.793650913238525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "その人に……なっちゃう、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want her… to become her sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.843650925159454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 6.843650925159458
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 11.043650972843206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。その人がいれば勇気が持てるんなら\nその人になったつもりでも、勇気は持てますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. If having her sister nearby gives her courage‚\nthen if you pretend to be your sister‚ that should give you courage‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.510317639509841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 18.310317639509805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私が、お姉ちゃんに……なったつもりに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pretend to be my sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.31031763950984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 23.442743901411735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "私も、アイドルになりたての頃って\nたくさん不安もあったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was a rookie idol‚\nI also had a lot of insecurities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.27607723474503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "歌もダンスも、本格的なのは初めてで……\nでも周りはみーんな、凄い人ばっかりだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my first time doing proper singing and dancing.\nBut everyone around me was just so amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.942743901411706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 36.14274390141173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なんだ\nすみれちゃんでも、そんな風に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ okay.\nI didn’t know you felt that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.34274390141172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 41.34274390141176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも瑠依ちゃんに……そして優ちゃんに出会って……\n何かが吹っ切れたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I met Rui… and when I met Yu‚\nI was able to let it all go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.37607723474508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "比べるから自信が持てない\n自分自身がふわってしちゃうから、自信が持てない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being compared to them killed my self-confidence.\nAnd since I felt like I was invisible‚ that also killed my self-confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.64274390141171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 53.176077234745044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "それならいっそ\nその人に自分がなっちゃえっ！　……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚\njust go ahead and be those other people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.342743901411694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 57.60941056807831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "比べるんじゃなくて……なっちゃえばいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead of comparing myself to her… just become her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.60941056807836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 61.285442396004996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、近くで見ていて憧れだった瑠依ちゃんに\nなろうって思って、たくさん真似しちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ since I idolized Rui‚ someone who I’d seen up close and personal‚\nI decided I’d become her‚ and I imitated her a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.24146275122959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 67.6974831064542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "……真似……って、例えば？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Imitated? Like‚ how?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6974831064542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "仕草とか、考え方、練習のしかた……\n趣味とか、寝起きする時間とかかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her tics‚ the way she thinks‚ the way she practiced…\nAlso‚ her hobbies and her sleep schedule‚ I guess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 80.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "同じグループだからこそ\nいつも間近で観察して、たくさん真似して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because we were in the same group‚\nI was able to observe her closely and imitate a lot of her qualities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "私にもできる、私だってなれる、いつかきっと！\n……そうやって努力してきたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was sure I could do it. I was sure I could be like her‚ someday for sure!\nAnd when I put effort into it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 93.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "してきたら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you put effort into it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 94.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……結局、瑠依ちゃんにはなれませんでした\nえへへっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end… I couldn’t become Rui.\nHee hee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なれませんでしたか……\nでも天動さんは天動さん、奥山さんは奥山さんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you couldn’t become her‚ eh?\nBut Rui is Rui. And you’re you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 106.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そう、それなんです！\n結局、私は私のままだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! That’s it exactly.\nIn the end‚ I’m still just me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "でもその人を追いかけて、その人とは違う自分に\n成長できたって気持ちが、自信に繋がったと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But by striving to be like Rui‚ I was able to grow into a version of myself\nthat was different from her. And I think that feeling of pride gave me confidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 120.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女が言いたいのは、憧れの存在と自分を比べて）\n（落ち込むのではなく――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(What she’s trying to say is that you shouldn’t compare yourself to your idol)\n(and get depressed over it…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_09-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（憧れの存在へ自分を近づけようと努力する）\n（それが大事だ、ということなんだろうな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But rather‚ you should work hard to bring yourself closer to becoming your idol.)\n(I guess that’s the important lesson here.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 132.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
